CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. 16 reads: "Registration Team - There are many members of the NAACP "Get-out-The-Vote," team....while the right photo show (left to right): Raymond Curry, Elizabeth Taylor; N. Davis, Victor Perry; Phillip Gand; Abraham Ali, Dorothy Robinson and Elnora Harvey, all members of the team."
TitMainTitle: NAACP "Get-out-The Vote" team members, seated from left: Dorothy Robinson and Elnora Harvey; standing: Raymond Curry, Elizabeth Taylor, N. Davis, Victor Perry, Phillip Gand, and Abraham Ali, posed in front of brick buildings, possibly Terrace Village
